title: Serena Williams crashes tennis match between two random fans - Yahoo7
text:
Share Serena Williams crashes tennis match between two random fans - Yahoo7 Serena Williams was out for a stroll recently when she stumbled upon two guys playing tennis, and she couldn't resist joining in. Close Serena crashes random tennis match UP NEXT VIDEO Serena Williams randomly crashes two blokes' tennis match. Source: SnapChat Serena crashes random tennis match 
The World No.1 never misses an opportunity to get out on the practice court, even if that means playing with two randoms she doesn't even know. 
Even though she was wearing boots rather than sneakers, Serena walked over to the court and asked if she could join in on the action. Awesome from the World No.1. Image: Snap Chat 
Naturally the tennis fans obliged. 
After all, when the greatest of all time wants to play alongside you there's no questions asked. 
She hit some balls and posed for photos and no doubt gave the two fans memoies that will last a lifetime.
